WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:24.000
Shooting Stars by Polly Sweetman

00:24.000 --> 00:27.040
Lisa and Alice are friends.

00:27.040 --> 00:29.240
They are on a plane.

00:29.240 --> 00:31.240
They are watching a film.

00:31.240 --> 00:33.240
They are on holiday.

00:33.240 --> 00:37.240
They are going to an island in Greece.

00:39.240 --> 00:41.240
Look Alice.

00:41.240 --> 00:43.240
There's Matt Lapardi.

00:43.240 --> 00:45.240
He's great.

00:45.240 --> 00:47.240
He's my favourite film star.

00:47.240 --> 00:50.240
Our holiday is starting well.

00:50.240 --> 00:54.240
Matt Lapardi loves Claudia Carmen.

00:54.240 --> 00:56.240
She's his fiancée.

00:56.240 --> 00:58.240
They are going to get married.

00:58.240 --> 01:00.240
She's a film star too.

01:03.240 --> 01:05.240
This is the hotel oracle.

01:05.240 --> 01:09.240
Lisa and Alice are going to stay here.

01:13.240 --> 01:15.240
This is our hotel Lisa.

01:15.240 --> 01:17.240
It's nice.

01:17.240 --> 01:19.240
Yes, it is nice.

01:19.240 --> 01:22.240
I'm very happy Alice.

01:22.240 --> 01:25.240
We are going to see beautiful places.

01:25.240 --> 01:28.240
We are going to do interesting things.

01:28.240 --> 01:31.240
Will we meet new friends?

01:31.240 --> 01:35.240
Will we have an exciting adventure?

01:42.240 --> 01:44.240
This is beautiful.

01:44.240 --> 01:46.240
Look.

01:46.240 --> 01:49.240
The village is beside the sea.

01:49.240 --> 01:54.240
The buildings are white and the sea is blue.

01:54.240 --> 01:57.240
And there are fishing boats.

01:57.240 --> 02:01.240
Wow, look at that big hotel there.

02:01.240 --> 02:04.240
It's the hotel Astra.

02:04.240 --> 02:07.240
It's very large and expensive.

02:07.240 --> 02:11.240
Are famous people staying there?

02:11.240 --> 02:14.240
I want to see some famous people.

02:17.240 --> 02:20.240
Costas and Eleni own the hotel oracle.

02:20.240 --> 02:22.240
They love their hotel.

02:23.240 --> 02:25.240
They like their guests.

02:25.240 --> 02:28.240
They cook wonderful food for the guests.

02:31.240 --> 02:34.240
That was a wonderful meal Eleni.

02:34.240 --> 02:36.240
Thank you Lisa.

02:36.240 --> 02:39.240
What can we do on this island?

02:39.240 --> 02:42.240
You can do lots of exciting things.

02:42.240 --> 02:45.240
You must visit the museum.

02:45.240 --> 02:48.240
There are beautiful statues in the museum.

02:53.240 --> 02:57.240
Lisa and Alice are enjoying their holiday.

02:57.240 --> 03:00.240
Each day they swim in the sea.

03:00.240 --> 03:04.240
Each day they eat delicious food.

03:04.240 --> 03:08.240
Today the girls are in the museum.

03:08.240 --> 03:12.240
A guide is talking about a statue.

03:12.240 --> 03:16.240
Two other tourists are near Lisa and Alice.

03:16.240 --> 03:21.240
These tourists are talking about film stars.

03:23.240 --> 03:25.240
Look at this newspaper.

03:25.240 --> 03:29.240
Here's a story about Matlabardi and Claudia Carmen.

03:29.240 --> 03:32.240
They are visiting this island.

03:32.240 --> 03:34.240
They are making a film here.

03:34.240 --> 03:37.240
They are shooting some scenes here.

03:37.240 --> 03:44.240
Matlabardi and Claudia Carmen are staying on this island Lisa.

03:44.240 --> 03:49.240
The hotel Astra is big and expensive.

03:49.240 --> 03:51.240
Are they staying there?

03:51.240 --> 03:54.240
Will we see them?

03:58.240 --> 04:02.240
The next morning the sun is shining brightly.

04:02.240 --> 04:05.240
I'm going to go to the shops.

04:05.240 --> 04:09.240
I want to buy some postcards and some souvenirs.

04:09.240 --> 04:12.240
Do you want to come Lisa?

04:12.240 --> 04:13.240
No thanks.

04:13.240 --> 04:15.240
My hair is wet.

04:15.240 --> 04:17.240
I'll sit on the balcony.

04:17.240 --> 04:21.240
The hot sun will dry my hair.

04:21.240 --> 04:24.240
Lisa is on the balcony.

04:24.240 --> 04:27.240
The sun is hot.

04:27.240 --> 04:30.240
Lisa looks at the hotel Astra.

04:30.240 --> 04:34.240
It is a big and important hotel.

04:34.240 --> 04:37.240
Then Lisa sees two people.

04:37.240 --> 04:41.240
They are on the balcony of the hotel Astra.

04:41.240 --> 04:44.240
The woman is looking at the sea.

04:44.240 --> 04:48.240
The man is looking at the woman.

04:48.240 --> 04:53.240
It's Claudia Carmen and Matlabardi.

04:53.240 --> 04:56.240
Claudia is sad.

04:56.240 --> 04:58.240
Why?

04:58.240 --> 05:00.240
Mat isn't sad.

05:00.240 --> 05:03.240
He is angry.

05:03.240 --> 05:06.240
Now Mat is shouting at Claudia.

05:06.240 --> 05:08.240
He is angry.

05:08.240 --> 05:11.240
Claudia is angry too.

05:11.240 --> 05:14.240
She is shouting at Mat.

05:14.240 --> 05:17.240
Lisa can see Claudia and Mat.

05:17.240 --> 05:21.240
But she can't hear their words.

05:21.240 --> 05:26.240
Suddenly Mat pulls Claudia into their room.

05:26.240 --> 05:28.240
Oh no.

05:28.240 --> 05:30.240
This is terrible.

05:30.240 --> 05:33.240
Mat is hurting Claudia.

05:33.240 --> 05:36.240
What shall I do?

05:36.240 --> 05:39.240
Claudia and Mat are in their room.

05:39.240 --> 05:43.240
Claudia takes a gun from her bag.

05:43.240 --> 05:46.240
Lisa sees everything.

05:46.240 --> 05:50.240
Lisa hears the sound of the gun.

05:50.240 --> 05:53.240
Mat falls onto the sofa.

05:53.240 --> 05:55.240
Oh no.

05:55.240 --> 05:58.240
Is he dead?

05:58.240 --> 06:00.240
Claudia is on the balcony.

06:00.240 --> 06:03.240
The gun is in her hand.

06:03.240 --> 06:06.240
She sees Lisa.

06:06.240 --> 06:09.240
Claudia is looking at me.

06:09.240 --> 06:11.240
She has the gun.

06:11.240 --> 06:14.240
She is going to shoot me.

06:14.240 --> 06:19.240
She is going to kill me.

06:19.240 --> 06:23.240
I must find Costas and Eleni.

06:23.240 --> 06:27.240
They will help me.

06:27.240 --> 06:31.240
Lisa is in the hotel oracles restaurant.

06:31.240 --> 06:35.240
But she can't find Costas and Eleni.

06:35.240 --> 06:40.240
Suddenly Lisa sees a man and a woman.

06:40.240 --> 06:44.240
They are standing by the door.

06:44.240 --> 06:47.240
Please don't be frightened.

06:47.240 --> 06:50.240
We want to talk to you.

06:50.240 --> 06:52.240
Everything is okay.

06:52.240 --> 06:55.240
Mat is not dead.

06:55.240 --> 06:59.240
Claudia and I are making a film on the island.

06:59.240 --> 07:03.240
In the film I fight with Claudia.

07:03.240 --> 07:06.240
Claudia kills me.

07:06.240 --> 07:09.240
We practice our scenes in our hotel room.

07:09.240 --> 07:12.240
The gun is not real.

07:12.240 --> 07:15.240
Claudia will never hurt me.

07:15.240 --> 07:18.240
I will never hurt her.

07:18.240 --> 07:21.240
We love each other very much.

07:21.240 --> 07:23.240
Wow.

07:23.240 --> 07:28.240
Claudia, Carmen and Mat Lapardi are here.

07:28.240 --> 07:31.240
They are talking to Lisa.

07:31.240 --> 07:35.240
Lisa is having an exciting adventure.

07:35.240 --> 07:41.240
And I have six postcards and some souvenirs.

